3 pillars

principle #1:
Behave with integrity: practice what you preach, be transparent, live according to your principles

principle #2:
EQ: arwaress to hehavior, 
EQ starts with self-awareness 
be an aspiring leader 

principle #3:
accountability: take responsibilities for your mistakes, take responsibilities for your team's mistakes
weekly check in: the key to getting rid of diappointing surprises is regular course correction
It's better for you to give frequent feedback on small issues than rare feedback on huge issues
